WEBVTT

00:02:28.714 --> 00:02:32.830
and June 1, 2009 was the day
that we were meant to go to the stadium

00:02:32.830 --> 00:02:34.889
and try and get the president's attention.

00:02:34.889 --> 00:02:36.329
It's a national holiday,

00:02:36.329 --> 00:02:37.978
it's broadcast across the country,

00:02:37.978 --> 00:02:41.386
and I showed up at the stadium.

00:02:41.386 --> 00:02:44.380
My friends did not show up.

00:02:44.380 --> 00:02:47.753
I found myself alone,

00:02:47.753 --> 00:02:50.280
and I didn't know what to do.

00:02:50.280 --> 00:02:51.695
I was scared,

00:02:51.695 --> 00:02:53.865
but I knew very well
that that particular day,

00:02:53.865 --> 00:02:55.086
I had to make a decision.

00:02:55.086 --> 00:02:57.509
Was I able to live as a coward,
like everyone else,

00:02:57.509 --> 00:02:59.107
or was I going to make a stand?

00:02:59.107 --> 00:03:01.313
And when the president stood up to speak,